	(7057, 697827, 'Nicolas', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'ngnative9@gmail.com', '', '+12259751432', '4/21/2024 11:06:10 PM', '4/22/2024 12:05:33 PM', 'Website Mendoza', 'New Lead', 'Unkown', 'General Intake', 'CampaignName : Contacto InglésCaseType : General IntakeCellPhone : 2259751432Email1 : ngnative9@gmail.comFullName : NicolasLeadProvider : Website MendozaSummary : Mensaje enviado por el lead desde el sitio web (2024-04-22T03:06:09.424Z):Good evening,I am searching for an immigration lawyer who has any experience with representing clients for a C-2 visa before. I figured I should search in the New York City area. I am a law student in the US, but the visa is for my partner who is Iranian. Basically, my partner is a national of a developing country and her current standing makes nonimmigrant visas difficult. However, she has been invited to the UN Headquarters to be a rep. for a UN accredited NGO. The UN gave us an email letter of the event with some info, but said the immigration process is her responsibility, so we are looking for assistance. If you have had experience with these visas before, please contact me so I may hire you to help us.Thank you,Nic', 'Mensaje enviado por el lead desde el sitio web (2024-04-22T03:06:09.424Z):\nGood evening,\nI am searching for an immigration lawyer who has any experience with representing clients for a C-2 visa before. I figured I should search in the New York City area. I am a law student in the US, but the visa is for my partner who is Iranian. \n\nBasically, my partner is a national of a developing country and her current standing makes nonimmigrant visas difficult. However, she has been invited to the UN Headquarters to be a rep. for a UN accredited NGO. The UN gave us an email letter of the event with some info, but said the immigration process is her responsibility, so we are looking for assistance. If you have had experience with these visas before, please contact me so I may hire you to help us.\n\nThank you,\nNic', '', 2, 1, '2024-04-22 18:59:46', '2024-04-22 19:59:45'),
